[Guest 2]: bit understandable, but that they didn't even name it, right, they didn't name what is happening.

00:58:30.640 --> 00:58:34.440
[Amit Varma]: I think that is a cause for hope is really what civil society is doing.

00:58:34.440 --> 00:58:40.000
[Amit Varma]: And your cause for despair is what the institutions and just protect us are, you know, how they

